Hunan Daily and New Hunan Client News on July 25 (this reporter) On July 25, the large-scale media integration campaign "Go to the Village Live to Watch Poverty Alleviation", hosted by the Financial Program Center of the Central Radio and Television General Station, started from Xuzhou, Jiangsu Province. Two caravans carrying the 5G new media mobile cloud broadcasting system were seen by the live guests and slowly drove out of the scene.
General Secretary Xi Jinping pointed out that "2020 is a landmark year. We will build a moderately well-off society in an all-round way and achieve the first century goal. 2020 will also be the year of decisive victory in the decisive battle against poverty."
The large-scale financial media campaign "Go to the Village Live to Watch Poverty Alleviation" is an important measure of the Financial Program Center of the Central Radio and Television Station to do a good job in the publicity of poverty eradication in line with this important theme.
The operation will go into poverty alleviation villages in more than 20 provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government throughout the country, dig fresh stories of poverty eradication, directly attack the great changes in the appearance of villages and villages, and show how villagers can break through the predicament of survival and development and move towards the road to wealth.
